<li>It may contain <b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:No_original_research" title="Wikipedia:No original research">original research</a></b> or <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability" title="Wikipedia:Verifiability">unverifiable claims</a>. <small>Tagged since September 2007.</small><br /></li>
<li>It may not present a <b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Countering_systemic_bias" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Countering systemic bias">worldwide view</a></b> of the subject. <small>Tagged since November 2007.</small><br /></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
